1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,131
Days pass with no word.

2
00:00:02,131 --> 00:00:06,023
Then... a traveler arrives carrying letters.

3
00:00:06,023 --> 00:00:14,919
Mu Young is alive — deep inside the temple — and what he has found confirms Manji's WORST fears.

4
00:00:14,919 --> 00:00:21,777
Balrog, the creature Tristan sealed decades ago... is preparing to reemerge.

5
00:00:21,777 --> 00:00:23,815
Mu Young cannot leave.

6
00:00:23,815 --> 00:00:26,503
Someone has to keep watching.

7
00:00:26,503 --> 00:00:34,843
So he writes... and he waits... and he trusts that his letters will reach the surface in time.
